  <brief_title>Preoperative Diet Before Sleeve Gastrectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Regular Diet of 900 Kcal/Day vs Balanced Energy High Protein Formula vs Immunonutrition Formula: Effect on Postoperative Pain After Laparoscopic Sleeve Gastrectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
